not beers.

269
00:17:48,806 --> 00:17:51,113
Nope. Frozen mackerel.

270
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:54,899
Those yellowfins will gobble
them bad boys up, I guarantee.

271
00:17:54,986 --> 00:17:58,338
