grabbing the hook out his scalp

462
00:31:35,284 --> 00:31:37,808
and just screaming,

463
00:31:37,896 --> 00:31:40,420
like, ahh!

464
00:31:42,204 --> 00:31:46,948
I tried to help,
but I just couldn't get

465
00:31:47,035 --> 00:31:50,517
to the back of
